item.nocaet.blood_flame.clue: 至火焰大锅之路危机四伏。
item.nocaet.blood_flame.tooltip:
一半的人被付与火焰，
另一半的人被赋予血液——
神的血也吸引着外乡之人。
item.nocaet.fading_flame.clue: 前往大树的深处寻求火焰。
item.nocaet.fading_flame.tooltip:
即将在风中消散的火焰，蕴含着微弱的力量，
就算再微弱的火，也能点燃大树——
所以，去收集更多的火焰吧。
item.nocaet.atziluth.clue: 前往光与夜交接之城，学习如何证明自己。
item.nocaet.atziluth.tooltip:
感觉的收获者，我恳求您，请将您的恩典赐予我。
将烈焰之精华与灵魂之传说灌注在一瓶之中。
愿赫斯提亚的火种永不熄灭，愿人类的精神薪火相传。
item.nocaet.spark_of_cosmo.clue: 踏入熊熊燃烧的永恒之火中，去探索埋藏着的神话。
item.nocaet.spark_of_cosmo.tooltip:
来自亿万年前的太古宙，
来自一只传说中的不死鸟。
桎梏了灵薄狱中罪恶种族的火种，而今又将赋予谁新的心跳？
item.nocaet.spiritual_glow.tooltip:
辉光转眼逝，
刹那映星河。
item.nocaet.bz_flame.tooltip:
万米高空处处冰，
燃烧室里炽热火。
item.nocaet.quantum_fruit.tooltip:
A virtual plant materialized by the influence of the End.
It seems that the original cultivator wanted to let the plant spread all over the internet.
Why is there a lab under this town anyway?
item.nocaet.quantum_skewer.tooltip:
An obscure snack on the internet snack developed by Blast Burst Quantum Labs.
It's so unpopular that no one will recognize it in a few decades.
item.nocaet.blast_burst_quantum_skewer.t:
A popular snack on the internet highly recommended by Blast Burst Quantum Labs.
If it was sent back to the virtual world, it would be a hit all over the internet as expected.
Unfortunately, it can't. Now it's probably just a kind of fuel... Want to burn something?
item.nocaet.fire_in_time: A Flame That Exists At A Certain Moment
item.nocaet.fire_in_time.clue: Usually it is almost impossible to obtain, but it so happens that the deepest part of the space-time fragment stored in a certain laboratory has it.
item.nocaet.fire_in_time.tooltip:
It is by its nature a self-describing, self-deriving field.
Time is not a variable in the equation that describes it.
So it now exists in your hands.

You say this thing looks like a clock?
It's because you think it's a clock.
item.nocaet.floo_flame.clue: Don't let frustration control your next move.
item.nocaet.floo_flame.tooltip:
Floo powder is on fire,
it fills you with determination.
item.semishigure.flame_icaruswings.toolt:
If I don't take Master to Synapse now
No one will be able to
And we can never save this world Master belongs to
item.semishigure.flame_pyrotechnicraft.t:
The summer light ignites and drops
Can I fall in love with you?
item.semishigure.flame_semishigure.toolt: You can't let yourself be held back by common sense in TeaCon, right!?
item.semishigure.flame_icaruswings.clue:
At the very top of the monumental totem
Where the sun melts away the waxy wings
item.semishigure.flame_pyrotechnicraft.c: Fireworks, should we see it from the sky or the ground?
item.semishigure.flame_semishigure.clue: On the gate of the shrine that exists on both sides...
item.noceat.burning_book.tooltip:
Even if ██ ███ ███████
It will all be ████████ by ███████
item.noceat.burning_book.clue: The flame brings creativity, the flame destroys creativity.
item.nocaet.mysterious_meatballs.clue: Trials under the ruins of sickly city
item.nocaet.mysterious_meatballs.tooltip:
It's a classic but novel cuisine cooked in the Crock Pot.
It is cooked with a mysterious ingredient so it tastes a little off.
nocaet.flame.grant: O! %1$s hath receiv'd the %2$s, now the Tree burnes stronger
nocaet.scroll.tooltip.clue:
The Scroll guides the the Fire Keeper
with words on it...
nocaet.scroll.tooltip.empty:
The Scroll guides the the Fire Keeper
...but the power is gone.
item.nocaet.wooden_bar_with_spark.toolti:
Nuclear torches will also burn out one day
But there is still residual temperature
item.nocaet.wooden_bar_with_spark.clue: Find the torch where it is frequently used
item.nocaet.endless_flame.tooltip:
A flame that cannot be extinguished，
which burn on a soul for thousands years，
There's no end to the pain。
生き延びろ……
